elements.name: To verify Login functionality of Adactin Hotel with Valid credentials

steps.name: User enter Username ,Password and clicks Login button
User navigated to Search Hotel page

elements.name: To verify user can search a hotel with given credentials

steps.name: User has to be there in Search Hotel page
User selects the Location,Hotel,Room Type,No of Rooms,Check In Date,Check Out Date,Adults per Room,Children per Room and clicks Search Button
User navigated to Select Hotel page

elements.name: To verify user can select the hotel

steps.name: User has to be there in Select Hotel page
User selects the hotel and click continue
User navigated to Book A Hotel Page

elements.name: To verify user can book a hotel

steps.name: User has to be there in Book A Hotel Page
User enter Firstname,Lastname,BillingAddress,CreditCardNo,CreditCardType,ExpiryDate,CVVNo and click BookNow button
User navigated to Booking Confirm Page

elements.name: To verify user get Booking Confirmation Details

steps.name: User has to be there in Booking Confirm Page
User Prints OrderNo and clicks MyItinerary

elements.name: To verify user can see booked Hotels

steps.name: User has to be there in Booked Itinerary page
User checks the booked hotel and click Logout

name: To validate Booking functionality of Adactin
